(13, 53, 'Menu configuration', 'menu-configuration', '', '<p>As you can see in the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=10&amp;catid=9&amp;Itemid=151">Module positions</a>, this template has two positions that can be used as a full featured multi-level menu:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>menu</li>\r\n<li>bottom-menu</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Also you can place menus in the sidebars or other positions, but the two mentioned above will produce a horizontal multi-level menu in desktop devices, with an appropriate handle for hiding the menu by default when using it on mobile/tablet devices.</p>\r\n<p>To set up a menu position (considering that you have created a menu and menu items in the Joomla Menu Manager), you must:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Go to the <strong>Module Manager</strong>, located under <strong>Extensions</strong> of the administration of your Joomla site.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click <strong>New</strong> to add a new module.</p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/menu_01_new_module.png" border="0" alt="Add a new module" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Select <strong>Menu</strong> as the module type.</p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/menu_02_menu_type.png" border="0" alt="Select Menu as module type" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In the basic options, select the menu you created on the Joomla Menu Manager, but also make sure that if you''re using one of the positions listed above, you select the appropriate number of levels you want, and that you set <strong>Showw Sub-menu Items</strong> to <strong>Yes</strong>, so that the sublevels will be shown.</p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/menu_03_multi_level.png" border="0" alt="Show sublevels in the menu" /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 9, '2014-02-12 11:59:16', 75, '', '2014-02-13 16:37:01', 75, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-12 11:59:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, 11, '', '', 1, 34, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(14, 54, 'redSHOP setup ', 'redshop-setup', '', '<p>When you wish to use redSHOP and not having all the default Quickstart data added, we have created a special package that include redSHOP only with the template install.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This package will install redSHOP and the special  redSHOP product and category template styles for this specific template.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/valentine_redshop_1.png" border="0" alt="" /> </p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/valentine_redshop_2.png" border="0" alt="" /> </p>\r\n<p><img src="images/documentation/valentine_redshop_3.png" border="0" alt="" /> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>To read much more about how to configure and use redSHOP you can visit our <a href="http://wiki.redcomponent.com/index.php?title=redSHOP:Table_of_Contents" target="_blank">redSHOP documentation wiki here</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 9, '2014-02-12 11:59:36', 75, '', '2014-03-04 08:35:07', 75, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-12 11:59:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 13, '', '', 1, 73, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '')